\frac{1}{2}\frac{d}{dx}(3x^2 + 1) = \frac{1}{2}(\frac{d}{dx}3x^2 + \frac{d}{dx}1) = \frac{1}{2}(3\frac{d}{dx}x^2 + \frac{d}{dx}1)
